Class HistogramDownsampler

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.core.HistogramDownsampler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, Iterator<HistogramDataPoint>, HistogramDataPoint, HistogramSeekableView

    public class HistogramDownsampler
extends Object
implements HistogramSeekableView, HistogramDataPoint
    Iterator that downsamples histogram data points using an HistogramAggregation.
